<style type="text/css">
  table {
    width: 100%;
  }

  table,
  th,
  td {
    border: 1px solid black;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    text-align: left;
  }

  th {
    background-color: aquamarine;
  }

  #textAlignRight {
    text-align: right;
  }
</style>

<div id="container">
  <p>Hello <%= studentName %>, </p>
  <p>Here is your weekly attendance report.</p>

  <% courses.forEach(course=> { %>
    <br />
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Course code</th>
          <% course.attendances.forEach(attendance=> { %>
            <th id="textAlignRight">
              <%= attendance.date %>
            </th>
            <% }) %>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td>
            <%= course.courseCode %>
          </td>
          <% course.attendances.forEach(attendance=> { %>
            <td id="textAlignRight">
              <%= attendance.hour==null ? 'x' : attendance.hour %>
            </td>
            <% }) %>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <% }) %>
      <br />
      <p>Please note that if your checking hour was too late, it's probably because there was an issue that day. Don't worry.</p>
      <p>If you have any question, you can directly contact your instructor.</p>
      <p>Best regards,</p>
      <p>Presence.</p>
      <i>---</i>
      <i>This is automatic email. You are receiving this because you're a part of greater good.</i>
      <i>If you have any idea for improving our system, you can help us by replying :D</i>
      <!-- 
    Hello {name},
    Here is your weekly attendance ({week# or date-date}) report:
    <ul>
      <li> {courseName, time, room}: {isPresent} -> {Warning or Praise}
      ...
    </ul>
    Overall, {good job or be careful}
    Signature
   -->
</div>